{"title":"白衣颂","authors":["黄苗子"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":5,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"白衣颂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄苗子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风三月三，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正待观桃李，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁知天降殃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"萨斯势披靡；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"播传冠状菌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涂毒无远迩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不论老中青，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华人及老外，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不幸而中招，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传播及邻里；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人心正惶惶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谣言日盈耳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或云要封城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或云缺盐米，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或云醋可治，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奸商大欢喜……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此时为政者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决策定宗旨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“苟能利国家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何惜生死以”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亿众呼应之，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一雪因循耻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壮哉医药师，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日夜无休止；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挺身第一线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白衣多仙子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矢溺唾涎污，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扶持近尺咫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十四小时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无休亦无寐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"非典渐得控，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"医护皆勇义。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所赖透明度，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传媒与电视，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"事迹太感人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"观之频掩涕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我友业记者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电访某护士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问女何所思？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“天地有正气”；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问女何所忆？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“病床与轮椅”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人有慈爱心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所以禽兽异。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"患难见忠良，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昔人有明示；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人定终胜天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此话是真理，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何曾大活人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竟被尿憋死。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华夏好子孙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堂堂对青史，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亿众一条心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚持是胜利！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":15,"page_end":15}